summary:
Go on an Adventure with Sara :)

Sara is staying at The Drunken Huntsman or Dragonsreach in Whiterun.
descriptionHtml:
[img]http://i.imgur.com/bcQHv2o.jpg[/img]
Go on an Adventure with Sara :)

Sara is staying at [color=#98fb98]The Drunken Huntsman or Dragonsreach in Whiterun[/color].
She has no melee weapon. So feel free to buy weapons for her from your wallet.
She's Essential, and you can get married with her. Her body is UNPB.

If you can't find Sara at The Drunken Huntsman in Whiterun,
I'm afraid you should do Clean Install of Sara.esp.
Don't panic. She will be waiting for you.


[size=4][color=#98fb98]Strongly Recommended Mods:[/color][/size]
[size=4][url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/13457]Face Light by tktk1[/url][/size]
[size=4][url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/35303]Female Facial Animation by nao4288[/url][/size]
Follower Overhaul Mod Like [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/12933]EFF[/url] and [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/33002]FLP[/url]


[size=4][color=#98fb98]Default Outfit:[/color][/size]
[size=4][url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/39588]Noble Wedding Dress by urshi[/url][/size]


[color=#98fb98]About Her:[/color]
Sara can control electric shocks, and she has resistance to the magic by electricity.
She has a sense of fighting (Standalone combat AI).
[color=#75FFFF]She knows how to use two sword[/color].
She's skilled at One-handed and Heavy Armor, Destruction. Also Light Armor and Block.

You can always change from normal head to nekominis head that later. And vice versa. [color=#75FFFF]No need to clean install[/color].
The Drunken Huntsman <---> The Drunken Huntsman (Nekomimi)
Dragonsreach <---> Dragonsreach (Nekomimi)
